# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
# .env.example  — copy to .env for local dev
# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

# App
APP_NAME=qa-chatbot
ENVIRONMENT=development
DEBUG=true
API_V1_PREFIX=/api/v1
CORS_ORIGINS=["http://localhost:3000"]

# Database
DATABASE_URL=postgresql+asyncpg://postgres:postgres@localhost:5433/qa_chatbot
POSTGRES_PASSWORD=postgres
DATABASE_POOL_SIZE=20
DATABASE_MAX_OVERFLOW=40

# Redis
REDIS_URL=redis://localhost:6380/0
REDIS_TTL_SECONDS=3600

# LLM
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-your-key-here
OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-your-key-here
DEFAULT_MODEL=claude-sonnet-4-20250514
COUNCIL_MODELS=["claude-sonnet-4-20250514","gpt-4o"]

# Auth
SECRET_KEY=change-this-to-a-random-32-char-string
ALGORITHM=HS256
ACCESS_TOKEN_EXPIRE_MINUTES=30

# Rate limiting
RATE_LIMIT_REQUESTS=100
RATE_LIMIT_WINDOW_SECONDS=60

# Celery
CELERY_CONCURRENCY=4


# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
# .env.production.example  — copy to .env.production
# Fill with real secrets — NEVER commit .env.production
# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

# App
APP_NAME=qa-chatbot
ENVIRONMENT=production
DEBUG=false
API_V1_PREFIX=/api/v1
CORS_ORIGINS=["https://yourdomain.com"]

# Database — use internal Docker network hostname in prod
DATABASE_URL=postgresql+asyncpg://postgres:STRONG_PASSWORD@postgres:5432/qa_chatbot
POSTGRES_PASSWORD=STRONG_PASSWORD_HERE
DATABASE_POOL_SIZE=20
DATABASE_MAX_OVERFLOW=40

# Redis — with password in prod
REDIS_URL=redis://:REDIS_PASSWORD_HERE@redis:6379/0
REDIS_PASSWORD=REDIS_PASSWORD_HERE
REDIS_TTL_SECONDS=3600

# LLM
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-your-production-key
OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-your-production-key
DEFAULT_MODEL=claude-sonnet-4-20250514
COUNCIL_MODELS=["claude-sonnet-4-20250514","gpt-4o"]

# Auth
SECRET_KEY=GENERATE_WITH: openssl rand -hex 32
ALGORITHM=HS256
ACCESS_TOKEN_EXPIRE_MINUTES=30

# Rate limiting
RATE_LIMIT_REQUESTS=100
RATE_LIMIT_WINDOW_SECONDS=60

# Celery
CELERY_CONCURRENCY=8

# Server
WORKERS=4
PORT=8000
LOG_LEVEL=info
